<div class="section my-2">
  <h2>Tables</h2>
  <h4>The Default Table used in most pages in the site</h4>
  <img width="600px" src="assets/code-images/main-table.png" alt="" />

  <p>If table column contains much characters that ruins the table sizing</p>
  <p>Wrap that content with a div with the class limit-((limit-value))</p>
  <p>Table Limit value from limit-1 => limit-6</p>
  <p>the head cell content should be wrapped also with the same limit value</p>
  <img width="600px" src="assets/code-images/table-cell-sizing.png" alt="" />
</div>
<div class="section">
